snippet.title: Ryse: Son of Rome Official E3 Gameplay Demo
snippet.description:
Fight as a soldier.  Lead as a general.  Rise a legend.  Xbox One and Crytek immerse you in ancient Rome, where you will become soldier Marius Titus, fighting to restore the honor of Rome at any cost.

ESRB Rating: RATING PENDING
